Invocation Name: restaurant recommender
des: Need help deciding the next place to eat? Restaurant Recommender is your solution! Just open it up by saying "Alexa, tell restaurant recommender to give me a place to eat", and it will prompt you with a few additional questions about preferred cuisine, location, and price, and voila, it will produce a final recommendation suited to your tastes!
